# Test API Endpoints

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Request OTP
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/thai-id/request-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "thaiId": "1101700203451",
  "phone": "0812345678"
}

### Verify OTP (Demo mode - use "123456")
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/thai-id/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "thaiId": "1101700203451",
  "otp": "123456",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "phone": "0812345678",
  "lineUserId": "U-test-001",
  "provinceCode": "10"
}

### Create Consultation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/consultations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "test-patient-001",
  "provinceCode": "10",
  "chiefComplaint": "ผื่นแดงคันบริเวณแขน",
  "symptomDurationDays": 3,
  "redFlags": ["rapid-spread"],
  "imageUrls": ["https://example.com/image1.jpg"]
}

### List Consultations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/consultations

### Get Doctor Queue
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/doctor/queue?provinces=10,50